{"tid":2077740,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"西洋棋由白棋先走涉種族歧視？ 媒體訪問讓棋手氣炸","createTime":"2020-06-24T13:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T13:40:40.000Z","uid":28114,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"63c9715ad9311e2070574103a39c1bf8ab241ccb","tid":2077740,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:26:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/06/24/phpbT8K25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F06%2F24%2FphpbT8K25.jpg&h=629e5518&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有媒體就西洋棋都是由白棋先下，是否有種族主義含意提出質疑，惹怒西洋棋手。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n2020-06-24 15:27:58<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國非裔男子佛洛伊德（George Floyd）遭白人警察以膝壓頸致死，再度引發全球反種族主義的浪潮，各界也開始審視日常生活中是否存在著種族歧視狀況，有媒體認為西洋棋都是由白棋先下，是否隱含種族主義，惹怒棋手。<br />\n<br />\n綜合澳洲媒體報導，《澳洲廣播公司》（ABC）日前聯繫前澳洲西洋棋代表亞當斯（John Adams），想邀請他接受採訪，詢問西洋棋都是由白棋先下，是否也是一種種族主義的表現，讓亞當斯氣到立刻PO在推特上說，「ABC認為西洋棋存在種族主義，因為白棋總是先走，他們正在徵詢西洋棋代表的意見，討論是否需要修改規則。」<br />\n<br />\n亞當斯怒出，新型冠狀病毒引發了一系列事件，但卻驚訝地發現ABC在探討無關緊要的話題，底下的網友也紛紛表示，身為國家公共廣播機構，ABC應該把人民的納稅錢用在更值得關注的社會、經濟問題上。<br />\n<br />\n面對網友的質疑，ABC發言人回應喊冤，稱西洋棋規則一直是棋界討論的話題，ABC團隊只是就這項議題提出初步探詢，還未有專題訪談計畫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3207838\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3207838&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPgqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=239d5b41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3207838&h=6c4998e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3207838</a>"},{"pid":"649a5f9147d39b5dadc2266bfd203bc609494aee","tid":2077740,"uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:27:16.000Z","msg":"死左膠，咁黑白棋係咪都要改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d623ae0496b0f41f20c95cd2791475835d06d3","tid":2077740,"uid":8439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:29:22.000Z","msg":"以後用白棋係咪要讓三round先？唔係就racist"},{"pid":"40a85479393210e846e37f4a30d23e948b8d8ba5","tid":2077740,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:31:05.000Z","msg":"係街見到黑色車係咪可以扔爛佢"},{"pid":"376132a16a9ef5baeb2064e3892a6863a11f4777","tid":2077740,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5d623ae0496b0f41f20c95cd2791475835d06d3","tid":2077740,"uid":8439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:29:22.000Z","msg":"以後用白棋係咪要讓三round先？唔係就racist"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:32:03.000Z","msg":"以後無回合制 無先後之分 真正平等<br />\n同一時間郁隻棋 如果撞左 就鬥大力頂走佢隻棋"},{"pid":"8ecae0f54eef51db52e8edccccaa5d660a289d20","tid":2077740,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:32:34.000Z","msg":"包剪揼先咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d97e9a8439763cd516f6ae3108aad6c20291a220","tid":2077740,"uid":48064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:40:40.000Z","msg":"轉曬做黃色 反正黃種人係可以歧視既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}